; text-align: center; flex-wrap: nowrap; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n  <div style=\"flex: 1; padding: 0 15px;\">\n    <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0924\/4016\/6685\/files\/Design.png?v=1756819021\" alt=\"Design\" style=\"width:70px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:12px 0 6px;\">Design<\/h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; color:#555; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:0;\">\n      All furniture is carefully designed and planned for intended uses.\n    <\/p>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div style=\"flex: 1; padding: 0 15px;\">\n    <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0924\/4016\/6685\/files\/Material.png?v=1756819021\" alt=\"Material\" style=\"width:70px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:12px 0 6px;\">Material<\/h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; color:#555; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:0;\">\n      Material selection is based on longevity and design needs.\n    <\/p>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div style=\"flex: 1; padding: 0 15px;\">\n    <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0924\/4016\/6685\/files\/Production.png?v=1756819021\" alt=\"Production\" style=\"width:70px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:12px 0 6px;\">Production<\/h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; color:#555; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:0;\">\n      CNC precision guarantees perfect alignment on all parts.\n    <\/p>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div style=\"flex: 1; padding: 0 15px;\">\n    <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0924\/4016\/6685\/files\/inspection.png?v=1756819021\" alt=\"Inspection\" style=\"width:70px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:12px 0 6px;\">Inspection<\/h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; color:#555; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:0;\">\n      Checks at every step, to validate every component.\n    <\/p>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div style=\"flex: 1; padding: 0 15px;\">\n    <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0924\/4016\/6685\/files\/warranty.png?v=1756819021\" alt=\"Warranty\" style=\"width:70px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:12px 0 6px;\">Warranty<\/h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; color:#555; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin:0;\">\n      We trust our system and want you to also, that's why it's 10 years.\n    <\/p>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    div[style*=\"display: flex;\"] {\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 30px !important;\n    }\n  }\n<\/style>","color_scheme":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"image_with_text_CQrqTp":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_X3xh3P":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Smart Sofa Beds for Every Room","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_mpGGTU":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>At Luonto, we believe furniture should adapt to the way you live. That’s why our collection is designed to fit effortlessly into any home - whether it’s a spacious house, a cozy apartment, or even a tiny home.<\/p><p>Choose from <strong>space-saving sleepers<\/strong>, <strong>versatile sectionals<\/strong>, or a <strong>stationary fabric cot sofa<\/strong> that blends comfort with practicality. From clever layouts that maximize every inch of floor space to expansive sectionals made for gathering, our designs give you flexible options without sacrificing style or comfort.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"button_NJyeYQ":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_labe