id’s little experiments, our sofa is designed to handle it all. With easy-to-clean fabric and smart protection, you can simply wipe away the mess without stress. So relax, sip, and enjoy the comfort, we’ve got the spills covered.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["row_jH6p9i","row_BELfXA","row_cD8KLN"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.multirow.presets.name","settings":{"image_height":"medium","desktop_image_width":"medium","heading_size":"h1","text_style":"body","button_style":"secondary","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"left","image_layout":"alternate-left","section_color_scheme":"","row_color_scheme":"","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"image_with_text_AceYqg":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_yYGKkm":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Our sofas adapt to your style — any space, any theme.","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_7J7rjn":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Whether you love the clean lines of modern design, the cozy charm of a lived-in space, or the festive energy of the season, our sofas adapt beautifully to your style. See them transform from a simple, elegant base into settings that feel just like home - no matter your mood, theme, or occasion. Imagine it your way, and let your sofa tell your story.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["heading_yYGKkm","text_7J7rjn"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Bernhardt_Tarleton_3-Seater_Brown_Sofa.gif","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"","image_behavior":"zoom-in","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"image_with_text_waPCiz":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_cQ6dkc":{"type":"heading","se